hat when hate is given room to grow, it becomes all the more difficult to c=
ontain.&nbsp; Our Constitution guarantees people&nbsp;the right to say what=
 they want, but the federal government shouldn't be using taxpayer dollars =
to support it. That's why last week I introduced H.R. 3773, the Stop Anti-S=
emitism on College Campuses Act, which will rescind federal education dolla=
rs from any college or university that peddles in the promotion of anti-Sem=
itism at an event on their campus. With hate against people of the Jewish f=
